        <p>Chitai-Gorod consists of several practically independent development teams: one supports the website, while another focuses on the mobile application. Each team has its own design system, developed over years of work and tailored to its processes. We rolled out the new design across both systems, often in parallel, closely collaborating with developers.</p>
        <p>Chitai-Gorod is attentive to its audience: we frequently left several options specifically for A/B testing, and contentious decisions were always tested before launch.</p>
